            , not yet taken, on the <rs id="t16841008-19-cd87" type="crimeDate">20th. of April</rs>
                  <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t16841008-19-off88 t16841008-19-cd87"></join>
                  <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t16841008-19-off91 t16841008-19-cd87"></join> last, <rs id="t16841008-19-off88" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t16841008-19-off88" type="offenceCategory" value="kill"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t16841008-19-off88" type="offenceSubcategory" value="murder"></interp>
               between Nine and Ten at Night, did Kill and murder 
                     
                        <persName id="t16841008-19-victim118" type="victimName">
                           Elizabeth 
                           Fairbank
                        <interp inst="t16841008-19-victim118" type="surname" value="Fairbank"></interp>
