                  </rs>: likewise they were a second time Indicted for <rs id="t16841008-19-off91" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t16841008-19-off91" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t16841008-19-off91" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
               stealing the Money, Plate, Rings, and other Goods, of the said Eliz. Fairbank, and a Suit of Cloaths from 
                     
                        <persName id="t16841008-19-victim120" type="victimName">
                           John 
                           Vaughan
                        <interp inst="t16841008-19-victim120" type="surname" value="Vaughan"></interp>
